4 for Federal Student Aid to determine the level of need and eligibility for state and
5 federal financial aid programs. The amount of tuition waived shall not exceed the
6 cost of tuition at the institution less any state or federal grants received, which shall
7 be credited first to the student's tuition;
8 (33) Participate with the Kentucky Department of Education, the Kentucky Board of
